---
import Layout from '../layouts/Landing.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Fundament">
  <div class="about-hero">
    <div class="about-hero__inner">
      <h1 class="about-hero__title">About Fundament</h1>
      <p class="about-hero__body">
        Fundament is software for running an Autonomous Private Cloud. It is designed to provide
        organizations with a minimal, reliable foundation for running modern applications. Unlike
        traditional platforms that bundle every service by default, Fundament is basic at its
        &mdash; delivering only the essential infrastructure and orchestration layers &mdash; while
        allowing each tenant to extend their environment with exactly the services and tools they
        they need.
      </p>
      <p class="about-hero__body">
        On top of this foundation, Fundament serves as an internal developer platform (IDP):
        enabling developers to build, deploy, and operate applications with speed and confidence.
        Its API-first design, multi-tenant architecture, and focus on autonomy and scalability make
        it suitable for organizations that want cloud capabilities on their own terms; secure,
        reliable, and without unnecessary complexity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section__inner">
      <h2 class="about-section__title">Project status</h2>
      <p class="about-section__subtitle">Concept &amp; Development</p>
      <p class="about-section__body">
        The focus of the project is currently on research and ideation. Some initial PoC
        applications may be built to give shape to ideas and to provide early feedback from testing
        users.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section__inner">
      <h2 class="about-section__title">Organization</h2>
      <p class="about-section__body">
        Fundament is being developed by <a href="https://digilab.overheid.nl/" target="_blank"
          >Digilab</a
        >. Digilab is a technical innovation team and testing environment initiated by the Dutch
        government to facilitate secure, responsible, and standardized data sharing across public
        sector organizations.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .about-hero {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--semantics-dividers-color);
    background: var(--semantics-surfaces-background-color);
  }
  .about-hero__inner {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--primitives-space-64) var(--primitives-space-32);
    max-width: 800px;
  }
  .about-hero__title {
    font: var(--primitives-font-display-2-lg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--primitives-space-24);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--semantics-content-color);
  }
  .about-hero__body {
    font: var(--primitives-font-body-lg-regular-snug);
    color: var(--semantics-content-color);
    margin: 0 0 var(--primitives-space-16);
    max-width: 720px;
  }
  .about-hero__body:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .about-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--semantics-dividers-color);
  }
  .about-section__inner {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--primitives-space-48) var(--primitives-space-32);
  }
  .about-section__title {
    font: var(--primitives-font-display-4-lg);
    margin: 0 0 var(--primitives-space-8);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--primitives-color-accent-600);
  }
  .about-section__subtitle {
    font: var(--primitives-font-body-lg-bold-snug);
    color: var(--semantics-content-color);
    margin: 0 0 var(--primitives-space-8);
  }
  .about-section__body {
    font: var(--primitives-font-body-lg-regular-snug);
    color: var(--semantics-content-color);
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 720px;
  }
</style>
